snippet.title: Amber Heard Sia Backlash, Rihanna Hits Forbes, Demi Lovato Stalker
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Sia Backlash, Rihanna Hits Forbes, Demi Lovato Stalker
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

Sia has taken to twitter, showing support for Johnny Depp amidst his ongoing legal battle with Amber Heard. It seems the case has been full of twists and turns, and to no surprise, many have come out showing their support for Johnny, after tapes were released proving he was in fact the victim. In other news, Rihanna may have had a rough couple of days, but it seems she’s bounced back, as not only was her apology accepted, but she’s also made it onto Forbes Richest Self-Made women list, joining some very impressive company. And Demi Lovato is having some issues with her now ex-fiancé, and has decided to get in contact with some lawyers, as she’s looking for legal advice.
